Results of statistical comparisons of asymptotic length (L inf; SL, mm), growth rates ( K), and time-at-age-0 ( t
0 ) between populations inside MPAs (MPA) and associated fished reefs (FR), using the likelihood ratio method of Kimura [ 46].
div.p: Length values have been rounded to the nearest mm. Values for each variable in MPAs and fished reefs are provided, along with Ï‡2 statistics and associated p-values. Significant results are indicated by bold font.
